div.h4: A figure still needs to be built for the haunted house. The figure has to be a zombie.
div.h5:
Requirements:
• The zombie has to be as big as it is on the drawings. A square on the drawing is equivalent to a block in the building room.
• The zombie has to be the same colors as the drawings.
div.h6: Look at the drawings from multiple sides. Then build a zombie with the blocks below. At the bottom you can choose colors, move the camera and add or delete blocks.
Front From the side From above From behind
